== Description ==

Creates a group (metabox), then adds fields to it.

// add_metadata_group($group_id, $metabox_label, $additional_args = array())
// add_metadata_field($group, $field_id, $field_label, $field_type, $additional_args = array());

== Instructions ==

1. Upload `voce-post-meta` to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
1. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
1. Create post meta fields like this
```
add_action('init', function(){
	add_metadata_group( 'demo_meta', 'Page Options', array(
		'description' => 'Just some basic options.',
		'capability'  => 'edit_posts'
	));
	add_metadata_field( 'demo_meta', 'new_field', 'Demo Field', 'text' );
	add_post_type_support( 'page', 'demo_meta' );
});
```
